<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>WeAreFantasy</title>
      <!-- Latest compiled and minified CSS -->

      <script src="/assets/javascript/appNBA.js"></script>

      </script>
    </script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container-fluid NBATeamTable">
    <br>
    <br>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-info btn-lg" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">Table Legend</button>
    <br>
    <br>
    <input type="text" id="mySearchInput" onkeyup="mySearchFunction()" placeholder="Search for Players" title="Type in a name">
    <br>
    <br>
    <select id='mySelectedInput' onchange='myPositionFunction()'>
      <option value="" disabled selected>Filter by position</option>
      <option value="pg">PG</option>
      <option value="sg">SG</option>
      <option value="sf">SF</option>
      <option value="pf">PF</option>
      <option value="c">C</option>
    </select>

  </div>
  <div id='playerlist' class="container-fluid NBAtables">
    <div class="row nbafantasy">
      <div class="col-md-12" id="nba">
        <div class="panel-body beforeResponsive">
          <div class="table-responsive">
            <!-- put images here -->
            <table id='myTable' class="table table-bordered tableNbaFantasy">
              <thead>
                <tr style='font-size: 12px;cursor: pointer;'>
                  <th>Player</th>
                  <th></th>
                  <th>H/A</th>
                  <th>Position</th>
                  <th>Team</th>
                  <th>Opp</th>
                  <th>Condition</th>
                  <th>Details</th>
                  <th>ProjMins</th>
                  <th>Salary</th>
                  <th>Useage%</th>
                  <th>PPG/L10</th>
                  <th>PPM</th>
                  <th>OVP</th>
                  <th>ProjTeamScore</th>
                  <th>GameLine</th>
                  <th>ProjectedPts</th>
                  <th>Value</th>
                  <th>SalaryAdjust</th>
                  <th>RecentPerformance</th>
                  <th>PTsVPos</th>
                  <th>CriteriaRanking</th>
                  <th>ProjectedOwnership</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
              {{#each fantasyNBA}}
              <tr id='mytabl3'>
                <td>{{Player}}</td>
                <td></td>
                <td>{{HomeAway}}</td>
                <td>{{Position}}</td>
                <td>{{Team}}</td>
                <td>{{Opp}}</td>
                <td>{{Mycondition}}</td>
                <td>{{details}}</td>
                <td>{{ProjMins}}</td>
                <td>{{Salary}}</td>
                <td>{{Useage}}</td>
                <td>{{PPGL10}}</td>
                <td>{{PPM}}</td>
                <td>{{OVP}}</td>
                <td>{{ProjScore}}</td>
                <td>{{GameLine}}</td>
                <td>{{ProjectedPts}}</td>
                <td>{{Value}}</td>
                <td>{{SalaryAdjust}}</td>
                <td>{{RecPr}}</td>
                <td>{{PTsVPos}}</td>
                <td>{{CriteriaRanking}}</td>
                <td>{{Ownership}}</td>
                </tr>
              {{/each}}
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="suggestedbuttondiv">
      <div class="suggesteddiv">
          <button style='text-align:center;' type="button" class="btn btn-default suggestedbutton">My Suggested Players</button>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="suggesteddivshow">
      <div id="sizer">
          <a class='closesuggested' href="#">x</a>
      </div>
      <h4 class='suggestedPlayersh4'>My Suggested Fanduel NBA Players</h4>
      <div class="suggestedDivScroll">
        <ul class='suggestedPlayersNBA'></ul>
      </div>

      <br>
  </div>
  <!-- Modal -->
<div id="myModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
  <div class="modal-dialog">

    <!-- Modal content-->
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
        <h4 class="modal-title">Description of each column</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <div class="row">
          <div style='background-color: #9bdaf2; height:140px;' class="col-md-2">
            <p>Good to go</p>
          </div>
          <div style='background-color:#45b9e7; height:140px;' class="col-md-2">
            <p>Be Aware</p>
          </div>
          <div style='background-color:#1a93c3; height:140px;' class="col-md-3">
            <p>Be Cautious (I would be weary. Check other categories)</p>
          </div>
          <div style='background-color:#115f7e; color:white; height:140px;' class="col-md-3">
            <p>Stay Away (Really depends on other categories)</p>
          </div>
          <div style='background-color:#0a384a; color:white; height:140px;' class="col-md-2">
            <p>Red Flag(Every other category must be perfect for me to use)</p>
          </div>
          <br>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <h3>How I use the table, and what columns I look at.</h3>
            <p>You have to look at everything collectively. The columns I mostly look at are ProjMins, Useage%, OvP, ProjTeamScore, Gameline, SalaryAdjust, RecentPerformance, PtsvsPos, and CriteriaRanking. After that I find the best combo of players and throw them in a line. The key to using this table is Trust the Process and HAVE NO BIAS OPINION!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-12">

          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <p>ProjMins</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>ProjMins: How many minutes a player is projected to play</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <p>Useage%</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>Useage%: How long a player has control of the ball per possession (Anything above 30% (varies based on position) is in the clear. It is ok to go lower if other categories are good)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <p>PPG/L10</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>PPG/L10: Average fantasy points per game for the last 10 games</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <p>PPM(Points per Minute)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>PPM(Points per Minute): How many fantasy points a player gets per minute (Anything above 1.2 is in the clear. It is ok to go lower if other categories are good)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <p>OVP(Offense Vs Position)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>OVP(Offense Vs Position): How well the opponent defends that specific position (Anything above 1.0 is in the clear. It is ok to go lower if other categories are good)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <p>ProjTeamScore</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>ProjTeamScore: Projection of the Total team points</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <p>GameLine</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>GameLine: Projection of the Total game points</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <p>ProjectedPts</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>ProjectedPts: My Projection of points a specific player will score.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <p>Value</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>Value: Projected value of a specific player based on projections (Try to stay above 5.0 but it is ok to go below if other categories are good)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <p>SalaryAdjust</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>SalaryAdjust: Their last game salary compared to their current salary (Anything 400 and below is in the clear. Above 400 is a red flag. - is equivalent to a 0 which is great)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <p>RecentPerformance</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>RecentPerformance: Their last game compared to their average (Anything 10 and below is in the clear. Above 10 is a red flag. - is equivalent to a 0 which is great)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <p>PtsVPos(Points vs Position)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>PtsVPos(Points vs Position): Points allowed by the defensive position</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <p>CriteriaRanking</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>CriteriaRanking: The rank I rank players. 7-6 and 5 are good to go but anything below 5 is a red flag</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
